{"tid":646164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［50分鐘丁片］台灣蘋果哩段新聞好有問題","createTime":"2018-04-28T18:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T00:04:07.000Z","uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"39d106e9c75caa3f7444ce1ed778b0721e162c25","tid":646164,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"港姐戰恩客50分鐘影片疑外流　網友一看直說「就是她！」<br />\n<br />\n凡走過必留下痕跡！香港一名身材修長、長相甜美的女大生念書時不僅被封為是校花，數年前還一舉奪下香港小姐的頭銜，不過有網友近日在瀏覽知名色情網站時，偶然瞄到一段「港女戰恩客」的偷拍影片，驚覺女主角不論是身型、五官、說話方式都與這名校花港姐十分神似，影片外流後引發網友熱烈討論，「我一看就知道是她！」 根據香港八卦媒體報導，被影射是「外圍女」的港姐這幾年闖蕩演藝圈，靠著耿直、大膽、愛開黃腔的特色十分受歡迎、很有觀眾緣，還自封為「性愛女博士」，現在卻傳出有一段不為人知的黑歷史，網友扮演柯南比對影片中的賣淫女與港姐的各項條件，看完紛紛直說一定是她，「不可能會錯的！那臉化成灰我都認得！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n&gt;&gt;加入蘋果日報粉絲團94即時94狂！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/025409_55b23ab45b8292480f8e50563463b044.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F025409_55b23ab45b8292480f8e50563463b044.png&h=a86a978a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/025418_3cdf37508307df1a753921afa81d0a89.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F025418_3cdf37508307df1a753921afa81d0a89.png&h=4b5c0a5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/025419_d9ad5b524778d0fcc93452cf24d7f62e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F025419_d9ad5b524778d0fcc93452cf24d7f62e.png&h=8dc4d5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原片：<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.thisav.com/playvideo?id=354459\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.thisav.com%2Fplayvideo%3Fid%3D354459&d=cbdjA%2FXUYG%2BFZv9I0HHbrTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=95e0615c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.thisav.com/playvideo?id=354459</a><br />\n<br />\n好似暗示fyy,但擺明唔撚係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoj